<p>The following tables allow GMs to randomly generate a wide variety of specific magic items, and complement the item generation tables <Link to="/rule/magic_items">in the base rules</Link>. Note that these tables create masterwork versions of armor and weapons; if you want to roll up normal, non-masterwork items, simply subtract the masterwork cost from the base prices listed. If generated items prove too powerful (or not powerful enough!) for your PCs' levels, simply roll again!</p>
